ght Royalty Board just increased the amount to be paid out to songwriters; =
Spotify said the change isn=E2=80=99t material, but it certainly isn=E2=80=
=99t in the right direction either.

Spotify=E2=80=99s challenge is that music labels had the integration that m=
attered in the music value chain: new music and the back catalog. From 2017=
=E2=80=99s The Great Unbundling ( https://stratechery.com/2017/the-great-un=
bundling/?access_token=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6InN0cmF0ZWNoZXJ5LnBhc3=
Nwb3J0Lm9ubGluZSIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhdWQiOiJzdHJhdGVjaGVyeS5wYXNzcG9ydC5v=
bmxpbmUiLCJhenAiOiJIS0xjUzREd1Nod1AyWURLYmZQV00xIiwiZW50Ijp7InVyaSI6WyJodHR=
wczovL3N0cmF0ZWNoZXJ5LmNvbS8yMDE3L3RoZS1ncmVhdC11bmJ1bmRsaW5nLyJdfSwiZXhwIj=
oxNzAyMDM4MDI2LCJpYXQiOjE2OTk0NDYwMjYsImlzcyI6Imh0dHBzOi8vYXBpLnBhc3Nwb3J0L=
m9ubGluZS9vYXV0aCIsInNjb3BlIjoiZmVlZDpyZWFkIGFydGljbGU6cmVhZCBhc3NldDpyZWFk=
IGNhdGVnb3J5OnJlYWQgZW50aXRsZW1lbnRzIiwic3ViIjoiUnNldVlFOGpnSGVQcFdKZjFmQWI=
0QyIsInVzZSI6ImFjY2VzcyJ9.X5CXrPv-plBx8gwhO1H66InS6TwVtQLFWVB4T_WcQaM2sTx1C=
cGq1iAURbIsV6MSf6ErtX7VBVlHeiqSeX_3U9tAuRb6sqVduozNi90d4QniH_6mdkmMB0ehW0qV=
pzdozsKgZur-7cPQozKoc3kNF2IQ5Z4o08MCpczeaW1T0UHGDaorCczR7dH09ZUgtzkbpR3vNe7=
of9ZN1Gp2P13dSdfagOLAWfE3-uNFaBC51t3pdxl-PmbShGDNfcX8idgmIHMHVBC7wkNS7IVXwm=
_0LfX7s0IazhLxTn5Rnbl4gmRY6z-COKc4CiSWXZjGstfv2X3vsN4afuluVsGFQW7DMg ) :

The music industry, meanwhile, has, at least relative to newspapers, come o=
ut of the shift to the Internet in relatively good shape; while piracy drov=
e the music labels into the arms of Apple, which unbundled the album into t=
he song, streaming has rewarded the integration of back catalogs and new mu=
sic with bundle economics: more and more users are willing to pay $10/month=
 for access to everything, significantly increasing the average revenue per=
 customer. The result is an industry that looks remarkably similar to the p=
re-Internet era:

A drawing of The New Music Media Industry Model ( https://stratechery.com/2=
017/the-great-unbundling/?access_token=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6InN0cm=
F0ZWNoZXJ5LnBhc3Nwb3J0Lm9ubGluZSIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhdWQiOiJzdHJhdGVjaGVy=
eS5wYXNzcG9ydC5vbmxpbmUiLCJhenAiOiJIS0xjUzREd1Nod1AyWURLYmZQV00xIiwiZW50Ijp=
7InVyaSI6WyJodHRwczovL3N0cmF0ZWNoZXJ5LmNvbS8yMDE3L3RoZS1ncmVhdC11bmJ1bmRsaW=
5nLyJdfSwiZXhwIjoxNzAyMDM4MDI2LCJpYXQiOjE2OTk0NDYwMjYsImlzcyI6Imh0dHBzOi8vY=
